text: Hernandia didymantha is a species of plant in the family Hernandiaceae. It is found in Colombia, Costa Rica, Honduras, Nicaragua, and Panama. ==References== Category:Hernandiaceae Category:Near threatened plants Category:Flora of Colombia Category:Flora of Costa Rica Category:Flora of Honduras Category:Flora of Nicaragua Category:Flora of Panama Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot
